message.entry: Trailing input arguments must occur in name-value pairs.
Bin limits must be a finite and sorted duration vector with 2 elements.
Bin width must be a scalar duration, and must be positive and finite.
Bin edges must be a duration vector with at least two elements.
''BinEdges'' input cannot be followed by any of ''NumBins'',''BinWidth'', ''BinMethod'', or ''BinLimits''.
EDGES must be a duration array.
X must be a duration array.
Bin edges must be a sorted duration vector that does not contain NaNs.
